---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="FeatureSignals is built by two software engineers as a developer-first, open-source feature management SaaS."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600">About us</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Built by engineers, for engineering teams</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      FeatureSignals is a software-as-a-service product created and operated by two software engineers who have spent their careers shipping production systems,
      managing releases, and wrestling with opaque pricing from legacy feature-flag vendors.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
      <p>
        We started FeatureSignals because we wanted a platform that matches how modern teams actually work: fast evaluation, clear contracts, OpenFeature-native
        SDKs, and the freedom to self-host when regulations or economics require it. Our focus is reliability, transparency, and tooling that respects developers’ time.
      </p>
      <p>
        The product you see today—dashboard, API, SDKs, and documentation—is the result of that hands-on experience. We are intentionally small, which keeps us close
        to customers and lets us iterate quickly on the problems that matter in real deployments.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you run our managed service or deploy the open-source stack on your own infrastructure, our goal is the same: help you ship features safely,
        run experiments with confidence, and retain control of your data and your roadmap.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 text-sm text-slate-600">
      <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Business details</p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        <span class="text-slate-500">Legal / operating name:</span> FeatureSignals<br />
        <span class="text-slate-500">Business category:</span> Information Technology (IT) Services — cloud software and related technical services<br />
        <span class="text-slate-500">Contact:</span>
        <a href="mailto:support@featuresignals.com" class="font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">support@featuresignals.com</a>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-500">
        For contracts, invoices, or payment-gateway verification, use the same legal name and category above unless we have provided a registered entity name in writing.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/refund-policy" class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">Refund Policy</a>
      <a href="/shipping-returns" class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">Shipping &amp; Returns</a>
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
